<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich Nothafft zu Wernberg, Viztum in Niederbayern</head><p>Der Rat bittet wegen des an Pfingsten geendeten Waffenstillstands um Anweisung Weinmar Eckers zur Rücknahme seiner Ansprüche oder Austrag an den üblichen Gerichtsstätten.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_169" id="84v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_169_r2l16"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft ʒum <expan>vvermb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_169_r2l17">vıcʒtum Jn Nıder payern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_169_r2l18"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vıcʒtum als Jr vns nehſt auf <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brıef <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_169_r2l19">antwurtt habt / vvıe Jr vveinmar Eker <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hett ein gütlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_169_r2l20">ſteen mıt vns ʒu halten auf dıe pfıngſten <expan>nehſtu<ex>er</ex>gangen</expan> / vnd was </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_169_r2l21">eẅch ʒu antwurt wurd . wolt Jr vns wıſſen laſſen etc . Alſo <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_169_r2l23">wır aber eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ . den <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vveinm<ex>ar</ex></expan> Eker 
<add><ab facs="#facs_169_r2l22">noch </ab></add> ʒu <expan>weiſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_169_r2l24">vnd ʒu <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>rıchten</expan> . daʒ er dıe ſprüche gegen vns <expan>fall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> oder ſıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_169_r2l25">aber an recht von vns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan> laſſe . an den <expan>ſtett<ex>en</ex></expan> da wır das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_169_r2l26">bıllıch tun <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd dıe fehe darauf gen vns abtu . VVan wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_169_r2l27"><expan>hoff<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſtee</expan> ſelbs wol daʒ er vns <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſprüch wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_169_r2l28"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>trüg</expan> / Vnd tut darinn / als wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol getrawn . das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_169_r2l29"><expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc Vnd lat vns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> eẅr <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_169_r2l30">bey <expan>dıſ<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_169" id="84v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft zum
                            <expan>Wermb<ex>er</ex>g,</expan> vicztum in Nider Payern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vicztum, als ir uns nehst auf
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brief
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und geantwurtt habt, wie ir Weinmar
                        Eker <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hett, ein gütlich steen mit uns zu
                        halten auf die <app>
<note><q type="date">pfingsten
                                    <expan>nehstv<ex>er</ex>gangen</expan></q>19.05.1415</note>
</app>, und was ewch zu antwurt wurd, wolt ir uns wissen lassen etc., also
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir aber ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, den
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Weinm<ex>ar</ex></expan> Eker <add>noch</add> zu
                                <expan>weis<ex>en</ex></expan> und zu
                            <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>richten,</expan> daz er die sprüche gegen uns
                                <expan>fall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> oder sich aber an recht von uns
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan> lasse an den
                        <expan>stett<ex>en</ex></expan>, da wir das billich tun
                                <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und die fehe darauf gen uns abtu.
                        Wan wir <expan>hoff<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>stee</expan> selbs wol, daz er uns
                                <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> sprüch wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>trüg</expan>; und tut darinn, als wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol getrawn. Das
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. Und lat uns
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
                        antwurt <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en.</ex></expan> D<expan>at<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
